Package: quone
Title: R Interface to the Quone Compiler
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Quone", "Language Project", email = "noreply@quone-lang.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Quone Language Project
Maintainer: Quone Language Project <noreply@quone-lang.org>
Description:
    Installs and invokes the Quone compiler from R. The package provides a
    minimal interface for compiling, checking, and formatting Quone source files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/quone-lang/quone
BugReports: https://github.com/quone-lang/quone/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    utils
Suggests:
    styler
SystemRequirements: quonec (the Quone compiler; install via
    quone::install_compiler()), code/cursor/positron (optional editor CLI for
    quone::install_lsp())
